(5242, 'en', 3, 'fatalmagicquotesruntime', '<p>Serious configuration error detected, please notify server administrator.</p><p> To operate properly, Moodle requires that administrator changes PHP settings.</p><p><code>magic_quotes_runtime</code> must be set to <code>off</code>.</p><p>This setting is controlled by editing <code>php.ini</code>, Apache/IIS <br />configuration or <code>.htaccess</code> file on the server.</p>', '<p>Serious configuration error detected, please notify server administrator.</p><p> To operate properly, Moodle requires that administrator changes PHP settings.</p><p><code>magic_quotes_runtime</code> must be set to <code>off</code>.</p><p>This setting is controlled by editing <code>php.ini</code>, Apache/IIS <br />configuration or <code>.htaccess</code> file on the server.</p>', NULL, 1295250009, NULL, 0, 0),
(5243, 'en', 3, 'fatalsessionautostart', '<p>Serious configuration error detected, please notify server administrator.</p><p> To operate properly, Moodle requires that administrator changes PHP settings.</p><p><code>session.auto_start</code> must be set to <code>off</code>.</p><p>This setting is controlled by editing <code>php.ini</code>, Apache/IIS <br />configuration or <code>.htaccess</code> file on the server.</p>', '<p>Serious configuration error detected, please notify server administrator.</p><p> To operate properly, Moodle requires that administrator changes PHP settings.</p><p><code>session.auto_start</code> must be set to <code>off</code>.</p><p>This setting is controlled by editing <code>php.ini</code>, Apache/IIS <br />configuration or <code>.htaccess</code> file on the server.</p>', NULL, 1295250009, NULL, 0, 0),
